						<div class="postbody">You are right, all non-English European versions of Red &amp; Blue use MBC5, all US (and other English speaking countries) versions of Red and Blue and all Japanese versions of Red, Green, Blue and Yellow use MBC3.  <br /><br />Good luck with getting the FPGA to transfer the ROM to the SDRAM and your bankswitching.  Maybe you could implement Wisdom Tree's mapper!</div>

					
