					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p189819">Re: Gameboy FPGA Cartridge</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=189819#p189819"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Thu Feb 23, 2017 3:05 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
